      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated tofu</strong> to the pan and cook for 6-7 min or until golden and crispy – this is your <strong>crispy tofu</strong></p>",
