    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the tofu is cooking, combine your <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>remaining chipotle paste</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and <strong>cider vinegar </strong>in a bowl</p><p>Add 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and stir it all together – this is your <strong>chipotle dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> baby leaf salad</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper</p>",
